{"tid":776980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"石內卜對哈利說的第一句話，就預告了《哈利波特》的結局？","createTime":"2018-08-12T14:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T08:27:45.000Z","uid":194101,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c705867cc5ab1c5dbfdf68f7b25c1e2c76777021","tid":776980,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"細個睇Harry Potter 睇唔明 <br />\n唔知原來石內卜係一個咁深情嘅好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">石內卜對哈利說的第一句話，你還記得嗎？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n石內卜對哈利說的第一句話是「波特，如果我把水仙球根粉末倒入苦艾汁，會產生什麼效果？」<br />\n<br />\n這句話看似普通，實則卻意義深遠。<br />\n<br />\n水仙算是一種百合花，而百合花的英文是Lily，莉莉是哈利媽媽的名字。<br />\n<br />\n而根據維多利亞時代的花語，水仙花的花語是：我對你的遺憾和悔恨；而苦艾則代表：缺席、不存在，有非常強烈悲傷的意思。所以綜合起來不就代表：「我對莉莉的死很悲傷，感到後悔不已。」<br />\n<br />\n石內卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433d577c7fa317a43a8bee12818c774c97ad00d6","tid":776980,"uid":10009,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"過份解讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea321fbfcc7312e7bdab9a3fab41e4c91f1b77f4","tid":776980,"uid":9708,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/9/9e/%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E7%AA%97%E7%B0%BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F9%2F9e%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25AA%2597%25E7%25B0%25BE.jpg&h=c178aa6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62f1b509799f1d863d0232869f50f08e8c413935","tid":776980,"uid":57073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"